Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.18,0:01:34.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西斯迪纳各地正陆续发生暴动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.10,0:01:38.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,领民们闹起来又能怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.52,0:01:41.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他们很畏惧我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.06,0:01:43.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能出事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.11,0:01:46.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过叛乱之火一旦燃起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.90,0:01:48.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就有可能越燃越旺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.82,0:01:51.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,自称科尔内罗的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.99,0:01:56.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死罗西尼家的人带来影响果然很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.87,0:02:02.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上不断有支持提欧•科尔内罗的人聚集到马尔扎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.34,0:02:05.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那帮乌合之众
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.67,0:02:07.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我来一网打尽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.30,0:02:09.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻让我去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.97,0:02:12.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我来替萨尔瓦多报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.39,0:02:14.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定不止马尔扎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.47,0:02:18.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,周边的居民也会加入叛乱军吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.60,0:02:21.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,最好召集到足够的兵力再出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.73,0:02:24.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有这工夫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.11,0:02:26.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不朱泽尔说的对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.94,0:02:31.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,多尼召集三千…不召集五干士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.74,0:02:35.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,五干？信不过我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.08,0:02:40.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,萨尔瓦多就是因为只带了几百士兵才会丧命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.46,0:02:43.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果连你也被杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.08,0:02:44.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,罗西尼家会怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.84,0:02:46.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会那样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.34,0:02:54.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就怕万一  我可不想变成失去两个儿子的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.35,0:03:01.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了我准备好了就出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.77,0:03:09.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,除了镇压之外就没别的办法了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.90,0:03:11.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今哪还有别的选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.03,0:03:15.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一族一直逼迫人民服从
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.24,0:03:16.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,除掉反抗之人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.95,0:03:18.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一直是这样统治国家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.16,0:03:20.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果放松控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.71,0:03:22.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就只能等死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.17,0:03:24.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.71,0:03:27.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有缄默法则的旗帜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.05,0:03:32.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,多尼的话肯定能替萨尔瓦多报仇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.55,0:03:36.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧•科尔内罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.06,0:03:42.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我要让你用生命赎罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.78,0:03:50.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.36,0:03:52.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我又没地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.70,0:03:56.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算待在罗西尼家  萨尔瓦多也不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.70,0:04:00.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟他很宠你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.95,0:04:04.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,萨尔瓦多真是个好男人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.83,0:04:08.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,热情贪图所有的快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.88,0:04:11.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还从不追究我的底细
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.76,0:04:15.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何不回城里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为萨尔瓦多下过命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.14,0:04:20.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让我把跟提欧在一起的侍从杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.89,0:04:23.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没完成这个命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.27,0:04:25.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,杀手的原则？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.40,0:04:31.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了杀死提欧  佩提力克迟早会率军前来才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.40,0:04:32.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要临近战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.86,0:04:36.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧•科尔内罗和魔法师就无法自由行动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.61,0:04:39.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就趁这机会把那家伙引出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.99,0:04:41.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能赢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.16,0:04:41.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.25,0:04:46.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟那家伙身边还有狼人女孩嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.37,0:04:47.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.75,0:04:49.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  狼人双胞胎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.92,0:04:53.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那该不会是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.80,0:04:57.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此  需要我把狼人引开侍从吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.76,0:04:59.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你能行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.30,0:05:01.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.35,0:05:04.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那两只肯定会来找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.81,0:05:08.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀掉狼人  你杀掉侍从
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.15,0:05:12.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,杀完他们之后希望你能杀了提欧和魔法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.98,0:05:15.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了给萨尔瓦多报仇吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.03,0:05:18.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,当然也有这个原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.49,0:05:22.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我原本就很讨厌那帮人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.74,0:05:25.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一看就知道他们相互信赖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.50,0:05:29.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想吐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.22,0:05:40.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.80,0:05:42.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,再喊大声点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.43,0:05:44.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,召集到不少士兵了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.14,0:05:49.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯跟击败萨尔瓦多之前的状况主全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.81,0:05:53.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉人们越来越有想法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.44,0:05:57.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望有朝一日能在这里建城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.78,0:06:00.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,很小也无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.41,0:06:03.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,届时无论我拥有怎样的爵位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.41,0:06:06.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,唯独这个村子我想亲自治理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.08,0:06:08.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.75,0:06:12.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为此  必须让大陆的战争结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.13,0:06:16.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而在此之前  必须要打到罗西尼家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.80,0:06:17.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.63,0:06:18.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.68,0:06:24.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,多尼•罗西尼率领的军队似乎向着这边出发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.89,0:06:26.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,果然来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.81,0:06:29.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能把村子变成战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.10,0:06:31.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也出击吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.83,0:06:52.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.46,0:07:00.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是那家伙杀了妈妈的黑魔女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.84,0:07:01.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.68,0:07:03.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.10,0:07:06.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 突然有私事要办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.10,0:07:09.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们几个暂时离开一会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.98,0:07:13.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了干万要当心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.15,0:07:15.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.32,0:07:19.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,埃文他们有什么事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.03,0:07:23.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,去排除妨碍这场战斗的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.41,0:07:25.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.99,0:07:30.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那群人中心的人应该是多尼・罗西尼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.37,0:07:31.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.79,0:07:33.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,继萨尔瓦多之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.42,0:07:34.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,再失去多尼的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.08,0:07:38.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必罗西尼家的统治会产生决定性动摇吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要罗西尼家的人还是领主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.05,0:07:48.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就只能被掠夺毫无理由地被杀掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.64,0:07:52.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,实施这种统治方式的地方就只有西斯迪纳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.10,0:07:55.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们站起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.82,0:08:03.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要用勇气克服恐惧  在绝望中创造出希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.65,0:08:08.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们赢下这场战争 结束罗西尼家的暴政吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.37,0:08:13.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我们所爱之人为了应该守护的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.55,0:08:24.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,进军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.14,0:08:29.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真自大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.22,0:08:32.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,管你有多少军队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.31,0:08:34.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底只是乌合之众
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.57,0:08:41.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我要踏平你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.37,0:08:49.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,罗西尼的士兵们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.83,0:08:54.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候用你的血来展现忠诚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.39,0:09:16.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都可能妨碍主人的人都得排除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.35,0:09:21.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了你还要吧提欧•科尔内罗和你的主人也杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.61,0:09:22.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,休想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.11,0:09:28.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.45,0:09:32.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,黑魔女特制的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.17,0:09:47.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是那俩狗崽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.52,0:10:05.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,恶魔的结界可没那么容易打破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.99,0:10:15.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  盛宴开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.39,0:10:40.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  只会防守吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.65,0:10:44.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,活着战到最后的才是赢家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.95,0:10:55.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在裆下我的匕首的同时上毒吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.33,0:10:58.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,侍从需要同时完成多个工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.00,0:11:02.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还要考虑各种可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.29,0:11:41.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗之火很猛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.00,0:11:44.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,再过不久你们就动不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.21,0:11:49.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后一动不动地被恶魔干吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.26,0:11:51.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会先撕碎你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.43,0:11:54.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们绝对会为妈妈报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.89,0:11:56.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,前提是有那本事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.14,0:11:58.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 艾玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.35,0:12:01.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,恶魔周围有屏障
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.40,0:12:06.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,试试那个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.36,0:12:10.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.78,0:12:12.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你们打算干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.34,0:12:34.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让她逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.88,0:12:36.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就只差一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.90,0:12:49.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,闪电啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.78,0:12:59.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.46,0:13:15.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们要去哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.55,0:13:20.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么为什么不战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.23,0:13:27.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,多尼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.02,0:13:32.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会陪多尼大人战到最后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.22,0:14:00.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,埃文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.51,0:14:01.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,埃文  快醒醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.35,0:14:08.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.14,0:14:10.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,别死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.73,0:14:11.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,埃文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.86,0:14:14.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,普莉希披
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.78,0:14:18.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他此时命不该绝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.21,0:14:33.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,埃文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.22,0:14:41.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我非得撕碎那帮人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.43,0:14:46.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我要撕碎一个人 陪我上路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.94,0:14:57.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,多尼大人 忠诚保住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.19,0:15:04.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋  你一直在等我疲惫吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.45,0:15:07.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我就只会这种战斗方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.04,0:15:12.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,小把戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.25,0:15:50.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.92,0:15:57.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,把这男人跟其他战死的人一起埋了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.63,0:16:02.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还有希望你号召罗西尼军的人投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.47,0:16:05.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,扫帚星  扫帚星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.72,0:16:08.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我的愿望能实现唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.14,0:16:11.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不不那是凶兆星哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.68,0:16:14.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,给人带来灾难的凶兆星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.23,0:16:15.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那光是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.52,0:16:17.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧提欧・科尔肉罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.98,0:16:20.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你就悲叹去吧埃兰姆的魔女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,流星流星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.57,0:16:26.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我的愿望定将实现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.89,0:16:52.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾雪拉把她抓起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.81,0:16:54.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.11,0:17:00.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,滚出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.15,0:17:04.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,罗西尼家持续了很多代的统治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.49,0:17:07.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,崩塌起来也是眨眼间的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.41,0:17:10.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧•科尔内罗的军队迟早会来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.49,0:17:14.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,届时就只能投降了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.96,0:17:16.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.71,0:17:21.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就肩负起西斯迪纳领主最后的责任吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.01,0:17:28.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你给我逃出这个岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.30,0:17:31.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你绝不能死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.72,0:17:32.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.47,0:17:35.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 快逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.69,0:17:39.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要是连你也失去了  那我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.82,0:17:44.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找提欧•科尔内罗谈判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.32,0:17:49.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我会试着主张自己对他们有利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.24,0:17:52.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就在他身上赌一把吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.45,0:17:55.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,把路让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.91,0:17:57.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我们打倒罗西尼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.69,0:18:22.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧・科尔内罗阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.44,0:18:24.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我名叫朱泽尔・罗西尼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.19,0:18:26.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟提欧阁下谈一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.82,0:18:28.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,佩提力克阁下呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.53,0:18:32.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲刚才将爵位转让给我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.83,0:18:36.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  由我全权负责此次谈判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.62,0:18:41.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谈判？究竟有什么可谈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.96,0:18:44.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了阻止无谓的流血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.88,0:18:48.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此那我就跟你谈谈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.30,0:18:52.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我方的要求是  侍奉罗西尼家的人的财产
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.05,0:18:56.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,以及生命的保障
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.60,0:18:58.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你方有什么要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.56,0:19:01.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,侍奉罗西尼家的人的全财产
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.94,0:19:05.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还有罗西尼子爵家的圣印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.19,0:19:07.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,佩提力克及你的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.53,0:19:13.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,把我刚才的回复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.37,0:19:18.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,当成揭竿起义的人民们说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.50,0:19:21.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我会谨记于心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.54,0:19:25.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要我和父亲交出性命无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.75,0:19:29.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过一旦将我们处刑领主有变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.72,0:19:33.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,宣誓效忠罗西尼家的人们想必不会坐视不理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.34,0:19:35.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我有一个建议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.43,0:19:39.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能否让我从属于提欧阁下呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.52,0:19:44.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要统治他们应该需要不少时间和精力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.77,0:19:46.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过只要有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.73,0:19:48.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他们一定会乖乖听话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.11,0:19:51.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这条件应该还不错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.74,0:19:52.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.12,0:20:00.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,单单为了方便统治让你从属
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.87,0:20:05.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样恐怕无法给起义的人交代吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.04,0:20:07.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.54,0:20:12.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我没想过毁灭罗西尼家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.63,0:20:13.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,通过这场战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.05,0:20:18.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解到有很多人愿意为罗西尼家效忠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.43,0:20:21.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了他们就让你活者吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.27,0:20:24.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从都是利用我这一点来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.60,0:20:25.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,两者听起来没区别啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.44,0:20:29.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这既是我的话 也是决心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.65,0:20:35.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经那个被称为英雄的杰德•科尔内罗最大的从属君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.66,0:20:37.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是罗西尼男爵家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.78,0:20:41.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我听说那时这座岛上的人很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.25,0:20:46.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想让西斯迪纳回到那个时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.71,0:20:50.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,起构筑曾经那个西斯迪纳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.71,0:20:54.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为此我想让你从属于我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.26,0:20:58.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.01,0:21:04.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过佩提力克得为这几代罗西尼家的行为负责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.94,0:21:07.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这一点无论如何都不能退让
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.19,0:21:09.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲原本就做好这个觉悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.48,0:21:15.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他早就认为罗西尼家的统治到极限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.03,0:21:18.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他同时也放弃了认为这无法改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.41,0:21:22.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过听过提欧阁下一番话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.83,0:21:24.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也改变想法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.87,0:21:28.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了这西斯迪纳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.00,0:21:34.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我从属于名叫提欧•科尔内罗的君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.17,0:21:37.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.30,0:02:47.59,shangzhong,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.95,0:17:57.58,shangzhong,,0,0,0,,喂  英雄科尔内罗来了
